cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a unified framework for the tasks of referring expression comprehension and generation, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses reinforcement learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The paper also deals with visual scenes, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper mentions end-to-end learning, which could suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
